snippet.title: NES Longplay [388] WWF Wrestlemania Challenge
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: JagOfTroy

Next in the line of pro wrestling inspired games comes this one, which has clear markings of LJN being involved with this project. Controls and gameplay are crap, the only saving factor being the music once more. The only recognizable themes to me however were the ones for Macho Man and Hulk Hogan, being slightly better than the versions done in the previous game. -
